Package edu.jhu.cs.oose.fall2011.cartagena.iface

Interface Summary
CartagenaModel This interface is implemented by those classes which represent games of Cartagena.
CartagenaModelListener This interface represents an observer pattern implemented over the CartagenaModel interface; it permits code to "listen" for events that occur in the Cartagena model and to react to them.
 

Class Summary
CartagenaIllegalMoveEvent Represents an event in which a Cartagena player has made a move which was deemed illegal by the Cartagena model.
CartagenaMoveEvent Represents an event in which a Cartagena player has made a move, thus changing the Cartagena model.
Location Represents a location in a game of Cartagena.
 

Enum Summary
Player An enumeration of players in the game of Cartagena.
SpaceType This enumeration describes all of the types of spaces which appear in a game of Cartagena.
